    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in pristine, flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a total dream and has been garage-kept and loved. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very, very happy. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 45900.0,
