    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the S54-powered E46 M3. This unit features the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band and an unmistakable metallic rasp. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry for optimal lateral grip. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent throughout, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
