    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is rare to find on the market today. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a high-end ceramic coating and free from any swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of creasing or wear, while the dashboard and trim are entirely free of sun damage or scratches. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive logbook of every fluid change and inspection. It drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered, offering crisp gear shifts, responsive handling, and a whisper-quiet engine. Included with the sale are two sets of original keys, the factory owner\u2019s manuals, and a fresh set of premium tires. This is an uncompromising choice for a buyer who demands perfection and a 'like-new' experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
